summary: This mod adds Sherlock Holmes to Skyrim, in the College of Winterhold, as well as a series of small quests and a main quest. It is a WIP.
descriptionHtml: Sherlock Holmes is a spellsword who focuses mainly on magic. He lives at the College of Winterhold, and everyone there ignores him. \\\"Freak\\\", they call him.
author: Jamie Moriarty
